(2438, 1, '2017-02-13 11:01:17', '2017-02-13 11:01:17', '[tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" template_type=\"row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"50/50 Congress Goal\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f201\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\n\nWhen we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Reproductive Rights\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f080\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\n\nFor centuries and even for the most recent decades, the women\'s reproductive rights were treated unequally as opposed to those of the men.\n\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row]', 'BLURB2', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'blurb2', '', '', '2017-02-13 11:01:17', '2017-02-13 11:01:17', '', 0, 'http://ld-wp.template-help.com/wordpress_62359-sample/tm_p