5\" text_orientation=\"justified\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f10d\"]\r\n\r\n<h4>Equal Pay Program</h4>\r\n<p>Being a witness to how female managers get paid less than their male counterparts in the same department and holding the same positions, on a daily basis, raises my awareness about the equal pay issues. Thankfully, funds like this one do...</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_testimonial][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_testimonial admin_label=\"Testimonial\" author=\"Mary Blanders\" url_new_window=\"off\" portrait_url=\"http://iklassfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image34.jpg\" quote_icon=\"on\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#f5f5f5\" text_orientation=\"justified\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f10d\"]\r\n\r\n<h4>Reproductive Rights</h4>\r\n<p>As someone who is old enough to remember the times before the Roe V. Wade and how incredibly exhausting it was for women back in the day to exercise their harshest reproductive choices and rights, raising awareness about this issue is really something that I...</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_testimonial][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"68px||70px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\" custom_margin_tablet=\"46px||40px|\" custom_margin_phone=\"46px||30px|\"]\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<h2>Featured Projects</h2>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"o