 Applebaum\" position=\"Manager\" image_url=\"http://iklassfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image28.jpg\" animation=\"off\" text_alignment=\"left\" background_layout=\"dark\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nA Juneau, Alaska native, Mrs. Applebaum has come a long way since her high school graduation all the way up to getting a Brown University Master’s degree in Economics. Talented with the digits, she’s no less successful when it comes to managing the human resources of the company. Ask anyone at our office who is their personal favorite manager...</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Emily Bluesome\" position=\"Manager\" image_url=\"http://iklassfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image30.jpg\" animation=\"off\" text_alignment=\"left\" background_layout=\"dark\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nIf you’d ask any of our workers, who is the executive manager that they’re always looking up and living up to, most likely Emily’s name will surface. Having a vast and thorough practical working experience lasting for more than 18 years, Mrs. Bluesome is an ideal manager, who is always on time to handle either our company’s clients or our internal team workflow issues...</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Diane Beaton\" position=\"Manager\" image_url=\"http://iklassfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image31.jpg\" animation=\"off\" text_alignment=\"left\" background_layout=\"dark\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nIf you’d ever need to figure out a workaround for a complicated business problem, look no further than Diane’s desk for getting a thorough and all-rounded advice… She has been working in the industry for more than 20 years, knowing all the ins and outs perfectly and teaching each member of our team. Regardless of which exact type of a task does she...</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_team_member][tm_pb_team_member admin_label=\"Person\" name=\"Elisa Hansolo\" position=\"Manager\" image_url=\"http://iklassfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image29.jpg\" animation=\"off\" text_alignment=\"left\" background_layout=\"dark\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\nBorn in New York City, Elisa always felt a strong urge for being an ambitious overachiever. Eventually, by the age of 25 she already had received her first Wall Street executive position, making her one of the youngest managers in the company. With her overall work experience spanning over 2 decades, Mrs. Hansolo is definitely the kind of a senior manager we all...</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_team_member][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"50px||85px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"60px||60px|\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<h2>Countdown Timer</h2>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][tm_pb_countdown_timer admin_label=\"Countdown Timer\" date_time=\"05/18/2017 12:19\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffba00\" timer_layout=\"flat\" header_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\" numbers_text_color=\"#8261b1\" label_text_color=\"#8261b1\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_countdown_timer][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"50px||71px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_margin_tablet=\"50px||60px|\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<h2>Circles Counter</h2>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_circle_counter admin_label=\"Circle Counter\" title=\"Equal Pay Program\" number=\"75\" percent_sign=\"on\" rounded_bar=\"off\" circle_width=\"7\" circle_size=\"169\" bar_bg_color=\"#8261b1\" circle_color=\"#f5f5f5\" circle_color_alpha=\"1\" title_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\" number_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_circle_counter][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_circle_counter admin_label=\"Circle Counter\" title=\"Reproductive Rights\" number=\"25\" percent_sign=\"on\" rounded_bar=\"off\" circle_width=\"7\" circle_size=\"169\" bar_bg_color=\"#8261b1\" circle_color=\"#f5f5f5\" circle_color_alpha=\"1\" title_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\" number_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_circle_counter][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_circle_counter admin_label=\"Circle Counter\" title=\"50/50 Congress Goal\" number=\"75\" percent_sign=\"on\" rounded_bar=\"off\" circle_width=\"7\" circle_size=\"169\" bar_bg_color=\"#8261b1\" circle_color=\"#f5f5f5\" circle_color_alpha=\"1\" title_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\" number_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_circle_counter][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"54px||86px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"60px||60px|\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<h2>Number Counter</h2>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_number_counter admin_label=\"Number Counter\" title=\"50/50 Congress Goal\" number=\"250\" percent_sign=\"off\" counter_color=\"#ffffff\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" title_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_number_counter][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_number_counter admin_label=\"Number Counter\" title=\"Reproductive Rights\" number=\"302\" percent_sign=\"off\" counter_color=\"#ffffff\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" title_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\" number_text_color=\"#ffffff\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_number_counter][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][tm_pb_number_counter admin_label=\"Number Counter\" title=\"Equal Pay Program\" number=\"15\" percent_sign=\"off\" counter_color=\"#ffffff\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" title_text_color=\"#1d1d1d\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_number_counter][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"54px||86px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin_tablet=\"60px||60px|\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<h2>Accordion</h2>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][tm_pb_accordion admin_label=\"Accordion\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\n<p>\r\n[tm_pb_accordion_item title=\"50/50 Congress Goal\"]</p>\r\n<p>When we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.</p>\r\n<p>The facts will tell us, that currently, just under 25% of the Congress representatives and senators are female, all the while the percentage of women among the US citizens is the plurality - standing at a high mark of 52% of all the population.</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title=\"Reproductive Rights\"]</p>\r\n<p>For centuries and even for the most recent decades, the women\'s reproductive rights were treated unequally as opposed to those of the men.</p>\r\n<p>We are determined to do whatever it takes to uphold the progress on this issue that the Roe V. Wade Supreme Court\'s ruling have made years ago.</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item][tm_pb_accordion_item title=\"Equal Pay Program\"]</p>\r\n<p>The United States Constitution does state that it guarantees equal rights and prohibits any kind of discrimination in this country, for any citizen, male or female.</p>\r\n<p>Still, these days, in 2017, female workers earn, based on different estimations, from 75 to 92 cents on every dollar that a male employee earns. We are determined to fight that!</p>\r\n<p>[/tm_pb_accordion_item]</p>\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_accordion][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"100px|||\" custom_margin_tablet=\"60px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|tablet\"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section]', 'Elements', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '847-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-16 03:00:54', '2018-05-16 03:00:54', '', 847, 'http://iklassfoundation.org/2018/05/16/847-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
