_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" disabled=\"off\" disabled_on=\"off|off|\" padding_1_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin=\"10px|||\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Educational Programs\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f12e\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\r\n\r\nWhenever the gender equality is concerned, we can probably all agree that it all starts with our youth - the girls.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Equal Pay Program\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f00b\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\r\n\r\nThe United States Constitution does state that it guarantees equal rights and prohibits any kind of discrimination in this country.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"50/50 Congress Goal\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f201\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\r\n\r\nWhen we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Reproductive Rights\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f080\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\r\n\r\nFor centuries and even for the most recent decades, the women\'s reproductive rights were treated unequally as opposed to those of the men.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][/tm_pb_section][tm_pb_section admin_label=\"Section\" fullwidth=\"off\" specialty=\"off\" transparent_background=\"off\" background_color=\"#ffffff\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" inner_shadow=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" padding_mobile=\"on\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" width_unit=\"on\" make_equal=\"off\" use_custom_gutter=\"off\" custom_padding_last_edited=\"on|phone\" disabled=\"off\" disabled_on=\"off|off|on\" custom_padding=\"96px||87px|\" custom_padding_tablet=\"70px||70px|\" custom_padding_phone=\"50px||50px|\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"center\" 