l choice decisions by strengthening youth who face challenges to achieving personal success and in reaching their full promise to becoming contributing members of society. The purpose of the IKLASS Foundation is to make a difference in the lives of our youth and the larger community we serve.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||40px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_margin_tablet=\"||25px|\"] [/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" max_width=\"550px\"]\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Support the Community</h4>\r\nThe Foundation supports the mentoring efforts of the Alabaster - Pelham Alumni Chapter\'s GUIDE RIGHT PROGRAM and Kappa League that award and help students manifest the dream of attending college, and the Foundation desires to see every student achieve in every field of human endeavor.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_text][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||25px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"] [/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"||25px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"] [/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"center\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" max_width=\"550px\"]\r\n<h4 style=\"text-align: center;\">Empowering the Future</h4>\r\nThe IKLASS Foundation understands that many youth face challenges achieving personal success and reaching their full potential.  Therefore, equipping them with critical thinking skills and the ability to make positive personal choices will aide them in being contributing members of society.  The Foundat