(2486, 1, '2018-05-19 18:04:14', '2018-05-19 18:04:14', '[tm_pb_section admin_label=\"section\"][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_cta admin_label=\"Call To Action\" title=\"Kappa Alpha Psi Fraternity\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_background_color=\"on\" background_color=\"#991500\" text_orientation=\"left\" header_text_color=\"#ffffff\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_button=\"off\" button_letter_spacing=\"0\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\"] [/tm_pb_cta][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" /][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\" disabled=\"off\" disabled_on=\"off|off|\" padding_1_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" custom_margin=\"10px|||\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Educational Programs\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f12e\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\r\n\r\nWhenever the gender equality is concerned, we can probably all agree that it all starts with our youth - the girls.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"40px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_margin_tablet=\"30px|||\" custom_margin_phone=\"20px|||\"] [/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Equal Pay Program\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f00b\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\r\n\r\nThe United States Constitution does state that it guarantees equal rights and prohibits any kind of discrimination in this country.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#ffffff\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"40px|||\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|phone\" custom_margin_tablet=\"30px|||\" custom_margin_phone=\"20px|||\"] [/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\" make_fullwidth=\"off\" use_custom_width=\"off\" use_grid_padding=\"on\" width_unit=\"on\" padding_mobile=\"off\" allow_player_pause=\"off\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"off\" make_equal=\"off\" parallax_1=\"off\" parallax_method_1=\"off\" parallax_2=\"off\" parallax_method_2=\"off\" column_padding_mobile=\"on\"][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"50/50 Congress Goal\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f201\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\r\n\r\nWhen we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][tm_pb_column type=\"1_2\"][tm_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" title=\"Reproductive Rights\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"on\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ff8ed6\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#0362c4\" icon_placement=\"left\" animation=\"off\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_button=\"off\" button_type=\"link\" use_icon_font_size=\"on\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f080\" icon_font_size=\"35\" circle_size=\"90\"]\r\n\r\nFor centuries and even for the most recent decades, the women\'s reproductive rights were treated unequally as opposed to those of the men.\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_blurb][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"32px||92px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"62px||62px|\" custom_margin_phone=\"32px||32px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"] [/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<h2>Pricing Table</h2>\r\n[/tm_pb_text][tm_pb_pricing_tables admin_label=\"Pricing Tables\" show_bullet=\"on\" center_list_items=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" custom_button=\"off\" button_letter_spacing=\"0\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" button_letter_spacing_hover=\"0\" remove_featured_drop_shadow=\"off\"] [tm_pb_pricing_table featured=\"off\" title=\"1 Month Membership\" currency=\"$\" per=\"/day\" sum=\"999\" button_url=\"#\" button_text=\"read more\" header_font_select=\"default\" header_font=\"||||\" subheader_font_select=\"default\" subheader_font=\"||||\" currency_frequency_font_select=\"default\" currency_frequency_font=\"||||\" price_font_select=\"default\" price_font=\"||||\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_font_select=\"default\" button_font=\"||||\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" background_color=\"#ffffff\"]\r\n\r\nSign up and become a part of the solution, rather than empowering the existing problems by being inactive...\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_pricing_table][tm_pb_pricing_table featured=\"on\" title=\"3 Months Membership\" currency=\"$\" per=\"/day\" sum=\"999\" button_url=\"#\" button_text=\"read more\" header_font_select=\"default\" header_font=\"||||\" subheader_font_select=\"default\" subheader_font=\"||||\" currency_frequency_font_select=\"default\" currency_frequency_font=\"||||\" price_font_select=\"default\" price_font=\"||||\" body_font_select=\"default\" body_font=\"||||\" custom_button=\"off\" button_font_select=\"default\" button_font=\"||||\" button_use_icon=\"default\" button_icon_placement=\"right\" button_on_hover=\"on\" subtitle=\"Best Value\"]\r\n\r\nSign up and become a part of the solution, rather than empowering the existing problems by being inactive...\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_pricing_table] [/tm_pb_pricing_tables][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"100px||71px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"62px||62px|\" custom_margin_phone=\"32px||32px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"] [/tm_pb_divider][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n<h2>Testimonials</h2>\r\n[/tm_pb_text][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"off\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"31px|||\" custom_margin_tablet=\"62px||62px|\" custom_margin_phone=\"32px||32px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"] [/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_testimonial admin_label=\"Testimonial\" author=\"Joanne Stevens\" url_new_window=\"off\" portrait_url=\"http://iklassfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image32.jpg\" quote_icon=\"on\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#f5f5f5\" text_orientation=\"justified\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" saved_tabs=\"all\" font_icon=\"f10d\"]\r\n<h4>Educational Programs</h4>\r\nAs someone who was born way back in the 1940s and lived to work in the 1960\'s, I thoroughly understand how important it is to support the female education and empower the options and opportunities that our young girls should have...\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_testimonial][tm_pb_testimonial admin_label=\"Testimonial\" author=\"Janette Henderson\" url_new_window=\"off\" portrait_url=\"http://iklassfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/image33.jpg\" quote_icon=\"on\" use_background_color=\"off\" background_color=\"#f5f5f5\" text_orientation=\"justified\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" font_icon=\"f10d\"]\r\n<h4>Equal Pay Program</h4>\r\nBeing a witness to how female managers get paid less than their male counterparts in the same department and holding the same positions, on a daily basis, raises my awareness about the equal pay issues. Thankfully, funds like this one do...\r\n\r\n[/tm_pb_testimonial][/tm_pb_column][/tm_pb_row][tm_pb_row admin_label=\"Row\"][tm_pb_column type=\"4_4\"][tm_pb_divider admin_label=\"Divider\" color=\"#e5e5e5\" show_divider=\"on\" divider_style=\"solid\" custom_margin=\"68px||71px|\" custom_margin_tablet=\"62px||62px|\" custom_margin_phone=\"32px||32px|\" custom_margin_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"] [/tm_pb_divider][tm_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" 