(8, 8, 'post_tag', '', 0, 0),
(9, 9, 'projects_category', 'We believe that young girls all across the globe deserve a great education and an equal shot! This means that we put the educational programs front and center of our women\'s rights centric agenda here! The facts will tell us, that currently, just under 25% of the Congress representatives and senators are female, all the while the percentage of women among the US citizens is the plurality - standing at a high mark of 52% of all the population. When we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.', 0, 5),
(10, 10, 'projects_category', 'Our mission as we see it is to make sure that there\'s an equal opportunity for both men and women, whatever their field of expertise, work or aspiration is! The facts will tell us, that currently, just under 25% of the Congress representatives and senators are female, all the while the percentage of women among the US citizens is the plurality - standing at a high mark of 52% of all the population. When we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.', 0, 5),
(11, 11, 'projects_category', 'Still, these days, in 2017, female workers earn, based on different estimations, from 75 to 92 cents on every dollar that a male employee earns. We are determined to fight that! The facts will tell us, that currently, just under 25% of the Congress representatives and senators are female, all the while the percentage of women among the US citizens is the plurality - standing at a high mark of 52% of all the population. When we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.', 0, 5),
(12, 12, 'projects_category', 'The issues with an unequal pay for males and females, educational hurdles and so many other problems in our country make some working fields harder for women to succeed in than in the others... The facts will tell us, that currently, just under 25% of the Congress representatives and senators are female, all the while the percentage of women among the US citizens is the plurality - standing at a high mark of 52% of all the population. When we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.', 0, 5),
(13, 13, 'projects_category', 'With decades of the track record, chronicled by both colleges and federal, state officials, the issue of both on-campus sexual assaults and US-wide instances of this problem, the... The facts will tell us, that currently, just under 25% of the Congress representatives and senators are female, all the while the percentage of women among the US citizens is the plurality - standing at a high mark of 52% of all the population. When we are talking about the Congressional representation that women do have in this country, the words are not enough.', 0, 5),
